description-en_US-print:
Professional 24 inch DICOM calibratable display for medical image viewing fulfilling dedicated quality requirements for reproduction of images from CT, MRI, nuclear medicine/PET and cardiology as well as PACS referral.

- Factory pre-set DICOM gamma curve;
- Digital Uniformity Control (DUC) for enhanced spatial uniformity;
- Precise DICOM GSDF calibration using 3 internal 14-bit LUT;
- Backlight ageing correction;
- Compatible with GammaCompMD QA client software;
- Side-by-side mode to display two independent image feeds.
